snippet.title: One Last Breath - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look at the official trailer of One Last Breath, a unique 2.5D adventure where you will play as an incarnation of nature in a polluted, devastated world. BE ONE WITH NATURE and bring the Earth back to life.

Coming to all platforms.

Wishlist on Steam NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1835190/One_Last_Breath/

Follow us on our socials to keep up with One Last Breath!

Discord: https://discord.gg/uHmRzfC2v3
Twitter: https://twitter.com/MoonaticStudios
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/moonaticstudios/
